      <c01 level="series" id="d35de58f-c9e8-11e5-8f06-18cf5eb0caa7">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Professional Papers</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Professional Papers series (1.2 linear feet) includes materials which relate to her career in the Institute of Gerontology. The "Curriculum Vitae", in Box 1, is helpful in providing context for the rest of the materials. Most of the other materials, including "Correspondence," "Reprints, Reports, and Papers," and "Workshops and Symposia" deal with Coons' research in "milieu therapy," or the concept of the "therapeutic community." Of specific interest in this context is the material covering the "Ypsilanti State Hospital Project", found in Box 2.</p>
        </scopecontent>
